data.description: The home is a very spacious 3800 square feet, with 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. This home features a large and open great room with corner fireplace, large kitchen with tons of cabinet space plus breakfast bar, tile flooring, vaulted ceilings, and walk-in closets. The basement is complete with another large family room and gas fireplace, full bath, bedroom, flex room and storage. Home also includes a 2-car garage, mature landscape, fenced yard, auto sprinkler, and a brand new furnace.
